==English==

===Noun===
{{en-noun-reg}}, US slang

# The neutral gear when used while a vehicle is moving, especially when it is used to save fuel.  (This is illegal in some places.)
#:''He shifted his car out of gear, at the top of the hill, and coasted down in Mexican overdrive.''

